reviewText: this was marked region all but will not play

Supposed to be all regions. Will not play in A/1!!! The disc was in a cardboard sleeve, as stated, however it was shipped in a plastic bubble wrap envelope. How it made it to me in one piece, I'll never know!
we  cant  watch it  on are dvd  player  what  can  wee  do

This will play on my region 1 dvd on my laptop,  it will not play on my older bluray/dvd samsung player
This is a very underrated movie....one of the better christmas movies
